{"tid":303730,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"虐待動物正一仆街！！","createTime":"2017-06-30T11:44:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-05T02:20:25.000Z","uid":76831,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"851e0c228ee8ccc3c1676557c170fcd94eefc29f","tid":303730,"uid":76831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T11:44:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/30/194242_cd8943b467d1975458f15a9b927ffe7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F30%2F194242_cd8943b467d1975458f15a9b927ffe7e.jpg&h=540a7392&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隻狗伸手個畫面好慘好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解啲人可以咁殘忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n元朗發生懷疑虐狗事件！現場為大棠路南坑排村一間村屋，下午5時許，警方接獲村民報案，指村內28號一間單層村屋傳出惡臭且有狗隻哀鳴，從門窗縫隙往屋內望，見有數頭犬隻蜷伏地上，惟村屋大門被鎖上，懷疑有人虐待動物。<br />\n<br />\n警方和愛協人員接報趕至，警員破門入內，發現已有約9至10隻狗明顯死亡，另有6隻奄奄一息，正聯絡戶主和住客了解及調查事件原因。<br />\n<br />\n有村民指出，該村屋面積約百多呎，有一名70多歲的伯伯獨居，屋內雜物凌亂，惟多日未見伯伯出現。屋內不時傳來狗吠聲，有犬隻俯伏門隙透氣和伸手「求援」。"},{"pid":"17cf8ed9e4fcdc43f13b0bee1f8f05eca4459a1d","tid":303730,"uid":76831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T11:45:13.000Z","msg":"正一死仆街尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁多人死唔見你死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做乜要啲狗死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"635c30e95960bc450c189e31a0240dea7cfd75c2","tid":303730,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T11:47:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6eccacc43a2b12eb22da5f2e818aced4cdc6bd95","tid":303730,"uid":76831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T11:48:13.000Z","msg":"咁都負皮係咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"451d7ba72d16d457d22db6394e385f6fdfa173c1","tid":303730,"uid":76831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T11:48:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正一死仆街尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁多人死唔見你死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做乜要啲狗死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"